cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with image classification and utilizes both computer vision and natural language processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of language models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper proposes a novel method for utilizing common visual concepts, which could fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper validates its method on action-recognition datasets, which could also place it under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
